The rumor snowballed into a Twitter storm of dangerous narratives that linked the coronavirus to child trafficking and pedophilia.
The special featured a room packed with child sexual abuse victims, including Oprah, who says she was raped at 9 years old.
It’s like a scourge on humanity.”Clearly, Winfrey is taking a firm stance against child sexual abuse.
Yet, with the ammunition of a single conspiracy tweet, people took clips from the special out of context to make it seem like Oprah was defending child sexual abuse.
